msgid "Spiritual Seekers and Mystics"
msgstr "Ceumannan spioraidis is Mìoshtachdan"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Curious, introspective, open-minded, and drawn to "
"esoteric knowledge. They may have a strong interest in uncovering hidden "
"meanings or patterns in life. Occupations: Spiritual coaches, tarot readers,"
" astrologers, or individuals involved in New Age practices. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to lean toward spiritual or metaphysical beliefs. They may "
"see the tools as a way to connect with deeper truths or universal energies."
msgstr ""
"Roghainnean pearsanta: Curios, a-stiùiriche, co-dhùnadh, agus a 'dol air "
"eòlas eisoptir. Dh'fhaodadh gum bi ùidh làidir aca ann a shuaineadh "
"mìneachdan falaichte no phatranaidhean ann an beatha. Obiridhean: Coachdair "
"spioraidis, leughadairean tarot, astar, no neach a tha a' gabhail pàirt ann "
"an cleachdaidhean New Age. Sgìreil: Bidh e a 'dhol a-mach air creideamh "
"spioraidis no meta-spioraidis. Dh'fhaodadh gum seall iad na h-innealan mar "
"bhealach gus a ghabhail a-steach do bhrìathnan nas motha no neartan uile-"
"fhille."

msgid "Numerologists and Gematria Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Nuamair a' Gematria agus na h-òigrig"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Analytical, detail-oriented, and fascinated by the "
"relationship between numbers and language. They may enjoy decoding symbolic "
"meanings. Occupations: Freelance numerologists, writers on esoteric topics, "
"or hobbyists exploring numerology. Ideological Spectrum: May range from "
"those who view numerology as a fun intellectual exercise to those who "
"believe in its profound spiritual significance."
msgstr ""
"Roghainnean pearsanta: Analathail, air moimhneachadh air mion-adhbhailte, "
"agus a tha ga bhuaidh le co-fhreagairt nan àireamh is cànan. Dh'fhaoidte gum"
" faigh iad taitneamh ann a bhuaidh le bhith a 'dèanamh eadar-theangachadh de"
" mìneachdan simbolach. Obiridhean: Nuamair a' Gematria saor, sgrìobhadairean"
" air cuspairean eisoptir, no neach-spòrsail a tha a' sgrùdadh a' Gematria. "
"Sgìreil: Dh'fhaoidte gum bi e a dèanamh seòrsa eadar a tha a' coimhead air "
"a' Gematria mar eisimpleireachd cothromach a-mach às a tha a' creidsinn "
"a-mach a' Gematria ann an t-ionnsachadh spioraidis mhath."

msgid "Historians and Linguists"
msgstr "Reòraich agus Gàidhealaich"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Scholarly, methodical, and interested in historical or "
"cultural contexts of numerical systems like Abjad. Occupations: Academics, "
"researchers, or students studying Middle Eastern languages, history, or "
"religious texts. Ideological Spectrum: Likely to approach the tools from a "
"secular, academic perspective, focusing on their historical or linguistic "
"significance."
msgstr ""
"Roghainnean pearsanta: Sgòraidh, dòichte, agus ann a tha a' coimhead air "
"còstaichean seandachdail no cultarail de shìocaman àireamhach leithid Abjad."
" Obiridhean: Acadèamach, rannsachaidh, no didealan a tha ag ionnsachadh "
"cànanan Meadhan-Eorpa, eachdraidh, no sgrìobhadh reilig. Sgìreil: Bidh e a "
"'dèanamh seòrsa ann an deagh-mhothachadh seacaraidh, acadèamach, a' sùil air"
" an t-àireachd seandachdail no cànain."

msgid "Religious or Faith-Based Individuals"
msgstr "Neach reilig no Creideamh"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Devout, reflective, and seeking deeper connections to "
"their faith. They may use the tools to explore religious texts or divine "
"messages. Occupations: Religious scholars, imams, priests, or laypeople with"
" a strong interest in their faith’s mystical traditions. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to have a traditional or conservative worldview, using the "
"tools to reinforce their spiritual beliefs."
msgstr ""
"Roghainnean pearsanta: Tha ann a bhith a 'creideamh, a 'nochdadh, agus a "
"'sgùir a ghabhail a-steach nas motha ri a' chreideamh. Dh'fhaoidte gum bi "
"iad a' cleachdadh na h-innealan airson sgrìobhadh reilig no teachdaireachdan"
" neòthaichte. Obiridhean: Sgòraidh reilig, imam, neach-pàiste, no neach-lèis"
" a tha ann a 'coimhead ann a ghabhail a-steach ann an trìobhaidhean "
"mhìoshtach a' chreideamh. Sgìreil: Bidh e a 'coimhead ann a bhith a "
"'coimhead ann a ghabhail a-steach a' chreideamh spioraidis, a' cleachdadh na"
" h-innealan airson a chùram."

msgid "Writers and Artists"
msgstr "Sgrìobhadairean agus Ealain"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Creative, imaginative, and drawn to symbolic or abstract"
" concepts. They may use the tools for inspiration or to add layers of "
"meaning to their work. Occupations: Authors, poets, visual artists, or "
"musicians. Ideological Spectrum: May range from secular creatives to those "
"with a spiritual or mystical bent."
msgstr ""
"Roghainnean pearsanta: Cruthachail, dìomhair, agus a 'dol air cuspairean "
"simbolach no abairt. Dh'fhaoidte gum bi iad a' cleachdadh na h-innealan "
"airson ionnsaidheachd no gus taighean de mìneachadh a chur air obair. "
"Obiridhean: Ùghdaraich, lathaich, ealain lèirsinneach, no iolachdan. "
"Sgìreil: Dh'fhaoidte gum bi e a dèanamh seòrsa eadar cruthachail secailteach"
" agus neach-spioraidis no mhìoshtach."

msgid "Puzzle and Riddle Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Na h-ògair Pàiste is Rìgh"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Playful, intellectually curious, and enjoy solving "
"complex problems or decoding patterns. Occupations: Hobbyists, puzzle "
"designers, or educators. Ideological Spectrum: Likely to approach the tools "
"as a form of entertainment or mental exercise, with little ideological "
"attachment."
msgstr ""
"Roghainnean pearsanta: Cròba, a tha a 'coimhead ann a ghabhail a-steach, "
"agus a 'nochdadh a 'slànachadh nan prìomh-bhuidh no a bhualadh "
"phatranaidhean. Obiridhean: Na h-ògair, na h-èistearan pàiste, no na "
"h-iongnaraich. Sgìreil: Bidh e a 'dèanamh seòrsa ann a ghabhail a-steach a' "
"bhuidheann mar foirm de bhlaigheantas no cleachdadh-coinne, le beag nas seo."

msgid "Conspiracy Theorists and Alternative Thinkers"
msgstr "Ceartan-ùghdaraich agus Nòinneadairean eile"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Skeptical of mainstream narratives, drawn to uncovering "
"hidden truths or patterns in systems. Occupations: Independent researchers, "
"bloggers, or activists. Ideological Spectrum: May have a more radical or "
"unconventional worldview, using the tools to support alternative theories or"
" narratives."
msgstr ""
"Roghainnean pearsanta: Skeptical de na narraidhean co-nòra, a 'dol a-mach a'"
" toirt a-steach briathran falaichte no phatranaidhean ann a' chuspair. "
"Obiridhean: Rannsachadh neo-iomadaich, bloigair, no eadain. Sgìreil: "
"Dh'fhaoidte gum bi e a dèanamh seòrsa ann a ghabhail a-steach a' ghabhail "
"a-steach a' ghabhail a-steach a' ghabhail a-steach a' ghabhail a-steach."

